{"tid":2453743,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《WSJ》：中國以國安為由 限制軍方、國企人員及政府人員駕駛Tesla汽車","createTime":"2021-03-19T16:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T11:59:37.000Z","uid":39464,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"fc93e9f28efb5326720714a2baf64280226c93b2","tid":2453743,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"《華爾街日報》引述消息人士報道，中國以國家安全為理由，限制軍方、從事敏感工業的國企，以及國家機構的人員，駕駛美國電動車生產商Tesla生產的汽車。<br />\n<br />\n報道指中國對Tesla電動車進行安全檢察後，發現車上的感應器可以記錄汽車附近環境的影像，Tesla公司亦可以取得汽車何時去過哪裏等關鍵數據。假如車主把手提電話連接汽車，Tesla更可取得手機內電話簿等個人資訊。<br />\n<br />\n報道指中方關注Tesla可能吧在中國取得的資料，送到美國，於是通知軍方、從事敏感工業的國企，以及關鍵國家機構的人員，要求他們停止駕駛Tesla汽車上班；部分官員和從事敏感工業人員所住的屋苑，亦禁止Tesla汽車進入。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210319/NTY5UBRD2NH4XGRWBFXDRJDXCU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210319%2FNTY5UBRD2NH4XGRWBFXDRJDXCU%2F&d=gmuJ%2FMz5RLkHlhSkJihz%2Bc5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=da0b3774\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210319%2FNTY5UBRD2NH4XGRWBFXDRJDXCU%2F&h=e089cd87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210319/NTY5UBRD2NH4XGRWBFXDRJDXCU/</a>"},{"pid":"9b76ae10777c229c6309e8697289f9cf6bd45d46","tid":2453743,"uid":55924,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T16:20:01.000Z","msg":"好人好姐做乜要偷睇你資料喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c963b8adaeaa60342e4f7e5ef4d039f88ed0c7ab","tid":2453743,"uid":23672,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T16:20:36.000Z","msg":"廠又起左 技術又偷左<br />\n已成condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46bd83a4e65ef812b623840e9a0bdd42107995c6","tid":2453743,"uid":194298,"like":9,"dislike":0,"scor